&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generalist business improvement consulting firm with a unique industry exclusivity philosophy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;40+ year history delivering high impact strategic &amp;amp; operational improvements to Fortune 100 clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Seven global offices: New York, San Francisco, Paris, London, Tokyo, Shanghai, Singapore&lt;/li&gt;
